inePortal&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=136903b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\n#香城online #黃店 #黃色經濟圈<br />\n#升呢  #抗爭日常化 #支持黃店<br />\n<br />\n黃店少一間就一間架<br />\n大家盡力而為啦"},{"pid":"6ff164015ed5ecc4fdaa3226310851416744e267","tid":1931783,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faaae644bb9d907ad93f8740009afcf17e94687","tid":1931783,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01397a37c6d020502ac399b1f2435326757d21ae","tid":1931783,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5dbec54a52c817d730f7421918c39cd7280b65","tid":1931783,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b835b8f3dc9bf766ef892df7dd8c7f2eaed0fb1","tid":1931783,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6c683bb61e7709ffdd2750bb0734d6f2c38fad","tid":1931783,"uid":227369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"524902de0be2d44b60e4ab0a9b7d7ae66d62a1e6","tid":1931783,"uid":112236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:06:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc5aee9b577dfd7e54